<P>
Rooney to Speak: "60 Minutes" commentator Andy Rooney, who was recently 
suspended by CBS for remarks attributed to him about blacks and gays, is the 
scheduled keynote speaker at the Constitutional Rights Foundation annual spring 
dinner May 7 at the Century Plaza. 
