traditional appetizers. Stella Papalos, Kapantzos' sister, above, samples meat 
as he begins carving roasted lamb. Desserts, right, include: Galactboureko, 
center; fresh fruit; red-dyed eggs and koulourakia, buttery twist cookies that 
may be prepared at home or purchased. Greek coffee accompanies. 
</P>
