ROYAL FAMILY; NEPAL -- ARMED FORCES; SHOOTINGS -- NEPAL; DEMONSTRATIONS -- 
NEPAL 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA041290-0095 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 203212 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
April 12, 1990, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
