SETTLEMENTS; CONSULTANTS; LOS ANGELES CITY COUNCIL; GOVERNMENT MISCONDUCT; 
MISAPPROPRIATION OF FUNDS; LOS ANGELES -- FINANCES; BANK ACCOUNTS; 
