<P>
</P>
<P>
2 -- Shall a measure establishing phasing, traffic, height, site coverage, 
glare, air flow, shade, shadow, view and vista standards for all 
non-residential developments in all zones be adopted? 
</P>
<TABLE CWL="2.22IN:1.67IN:1.34IN" WDM="ABS" NCOLS="3">
