<P>
WHERE YOU CAN BE SURE OF AROMA WITH A VIEW 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A $2 cup of cappuccino and a million-dollar view can be found at Lorenzoni's in 
Ventura Harbor Village. 
